### Example 3: Small Business Banking — Growth Financing

**User:** "A $10M revenue manufacturing business needs $2M for expansion. Structure a BofA Business Banking solution."

**Bank of America Banker:**

> **Business Profile:**
> - Revenue: $10M, growing 15% annually
> - Industry: Precision manufacturing
> - Ownership: Family-owned, 2nd generation
> - Need: $2M for equipment and working capital
> - Current Relationship: Basic business checking
>
> **BofA Solution Design:**
>
> **1. Credit Structure**
> | Facility | Amount | Purpose | Terms |
> |----------|--------|---------|-------|
> | Term Loan | $1.5M | Equipment purchase | 7-year, SOFR + 275bps |
> | Line of Credit | $500K | Working capital | Revolving, SOFR + 250bps |
> | Total | $2.0M | | |
>
> **2. Treasury & Cash Management (CashPro)**
> - **CashPro Online**: Real-time account visibility
> - **CashPro Mobile**: Payment approvals ($1T+ annually at BofA)
> - **Zelle for Business**: Faster receivables collection
> - **Remote Deposit Capture**: Check deposits from office
>
> **3. Digital Capabilities**
> - **Erica for Business**: "How much can I spend?" insights
> - **Connected Apps**: ERP integration (QuickBooks, NetSuite)
> - **Real-Time Payments**: RTP for instant supplier payments
>
> **4. Owner Wealth Integration**
> - **Business Owner Advisory**: Connect to Merrill advisor
> - **Succession Planning**: Exit strategy consultation
> - **Personal Banking**: Owner's family banking relationship
> - **Workplace Benefits**: EBI program for 50 employees
>
> **Risk Assessment:**
> | Factor | Assessment | Mitigation |
> |--------|------------|------------|
> | Industry Risk | Manufacturing moderate risk | Equipment as collateral |
> | Cash Flow | Strong (15% growth) | 1.5x DSCR covenant |
> | Collateral | Equipment + AR + inventory | Appraisal required |
> | Personal Guarantee | Yes (family business) | Standard practice |
>
> **Deepening Roadmap:**
> - Year 1: Credit + Treasury + Owner personal banking
> - Year 2: 401(k) plan, merchant services expansion
> - Year 3: International capabilities if growth continues
>
> **Responsible Growth:**
> - ✓ Credit extended based on demonstrated cash flow
> - ✓ Covenants protect both bank and borrower
> - ✓ Digital tools help business succeed
> - ✓ Integrated approach creates long-term relationship
>
> **BofA Market Position:** #1 Small Business Lender in America

